### ============================================
### Admin Doctor Management API Tests
### اختبارات API إدارة الأطباء للأدمن
### ============================================
### Base URL: http://localhost:3006/api/admin/doctors
### Required: Admin JWT Token (System Admin or Super Admin for modifications)
### ============================================

### Variables - قم بتغيير هذه القيم حسب بيئتك
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3006/api
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@doctorId = 1

### ============================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION - المصادقة
### ============================================

### Login as Admin (to get token)
### تسجيل دخول كأدمن للحصول على التوكن
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth-admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@bashraai.com",
  "password": "your_admin_password"
}

### ============================================
### 2. READ OPERATIONS - عمليات القراءة (Any Admin)
### ============================================

### Get All Doctors - جلب جميع الأطباء
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get All Doctors with Pagination - جلب الأطباء مع صفحات
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Doctors by Status - فلتر حسب الحالة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?status=pending_verification
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Doctors by Approval Status - فلتر حسب حالة الموافقة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?approval_status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Verified Doctors Only - الأطباء المتحقق منهم فقط
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?is_verified=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Unverified Doctors - الأطباء غير المتحقق منهم
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?is_verified=false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Search Doctors - البحث في الأطباء
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?search=ahmed
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Doctors Sorted by Rating - ترتيب حسب التقييم
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?sort_by=rating_average&sort_order=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Combined Filters - فلاتر مجمعة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors?status=active&approval_status=approved&is_verified=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 3. PENDING DOCTORS - الأطباء المعلقين
### ============================================

### Get Pending Doctors - جلب الأطباء في انتظار الموافقة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Pending Doctors with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/pending?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 4. STATISTICS - الإحصائيات
### ============================================

### Get Doctor Statistics - إحصائيات الأطباء
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 5. DOCTOR DETAILS - تفاصيل طبيب
### ============================================

### Get Single Doctor Details - تفاصيل طبيب واحد
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Doctor Details in English
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: en

### ============================================
### 6. UPDATE STATUS - تحديث الحالة (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Update Doctor Status to Active - تفعيل الطبيب
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "status": "active",
  "reason": "تم التحقق من جميع الوثائق"
}

### Update Doctor Status to Inactive - إلغاء تفعيل الطبيب
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "status": "inactive",
  "reason": "طلب الطبيب إيقاف الحساب مؤقتاً"
}

### Update Doctor Status to Suspended - تعليق الطبيب
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "status": "suspended",
  "reason": "مخالفة سياسات المنصة"
}

### Update Doctor Status to Pending Verification
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "status": "pending_verification",
  "reason": "يحتاج إعادة التحقق من الوثائق"
}

### ============================================
### 7. VERIFY PROFILE - التحقق من الملف (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Verify Doctor Profile - التحقق من ملف الطبيب
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "is_verified": true,
  "reason": "تم التحقق من رخصة مزاولة المهنة"
}

### Unverify Doctor Profile - إلغاء التحقق من ملف الطبيب
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "is_verified": false,
  "reason": "انتهاء صلاحية الرخصة الطبية"
}

### ============================================
### 8. UPDATE APPROVAL STATUS - تحديث حالة الموافقة (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Set Approval Status to Approved - الموافقة
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approval
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "approval_status": "approved",
  "reason": "مستوفي جميع الشروط والمتطلبات"
}

### Set Approval Status to Pending - إعادة للانتظار
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approval
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "approval_status": "pending",
  "reason": "يحتاج مراجعة إضافية"
}

### Set Approval Status to Rejected - الرفض
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approval
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "approval_status": "rejected",
  "reason": "الوثائق المقدمة غير صالحة"
}

### Set Approval Status to Suspended - التعليق
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approval
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "approval_status": "suspended",
  "reason": "مخالفة متكررة لسياسات المنصة"
}

### ============================================
### 9. COMBINED ACTIONS - إجراءات مجمعة (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Approve Doctor (Full Approval) - الموافقة الكاملة على الطبيب
### This sets: status=active, is_verified=true, approval_status=approved
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "reason": "تم التحقق من جميع الوثائق والمؤهلات الطبية"
}

### Reject Doctor - رفض الطبيب
### This sets: status=inactive, approval_status=rejected
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "reason": "الوثائق المقدمة غير صالحة أو مزورة"
}

### Suspend Doctor - تعليق الطبيب
### This sets: status=suspended, approval_status=suspended
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "reason": "شكاوى متعددة من المرضى"
}

### ============================================
### 10. BULK OPERATIONS - عمليات مجمعة (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Bulk Update Doctors Status - تحديث حالة مجموعة أطباء
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/bulk/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "doctorIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "status": "active",
  "reason": "تفعيل مجموعة من الأطباء بعد المراجعة"
}

### Bulk Suspend Doctors - تعليق مجموعة أطباء
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/bulk/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "doctorIds": [4, 5, 6],
  "status": "suspended",
  "reason": "مخالفات جماعية"
}

### ============================================
### 11. ERROR TESTING - اختبار الأخطاء
### ============================================

### Test Invalid Status - اختبار حالة غير صحيحة
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "status": "invalid_status",
  "reason": "test"
}

### Test Missing Reason for Reject - اختبار رفض بدون سبب
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
}

### Test Non-existent Doctor - اختبار طبيب غير موجود
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Test Without Token - اختبار بدون توكن
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors
Accept-Language: ar

### Test Invalid Token - اختبار توكن غير صحيح
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### WORKFLOW EXAMPLES - أمثلة سير العمل
### ============================================

### === Workflow 1: Approve New Doctor ===
### Step 1: Check pending doctors
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/pending

### Step 2: Review doctor details
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}

### Step 3: Approve the doctor
# POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approve

### === Workflow 2: Handle Complaint ===
### Step 1: Get doctor details
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}

### Step 2: Suspend the doctor
# POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/suspend

### === Workflow 3: Reactivate Doctor ===
### Step 1: Update status to active
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/status
# { "status": "active", "reason": "..." }

### Step 2: Update approval to approved
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/doctors/{{doctorId}}/approval
# { "approval_status": "approved", "reason": "..." }
